WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: sl

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Translator: Nika Kotnik
Reviewer: Klavdija Cernilogar

00:00:16.582 --> 00:00:21.525
Petič stojim na tej obali,

00:00:21.525 --> 00:00:23.601
na obali Kube,

00:00:23.601 --> 00:00:28.189
gledam oddaljeno obzorje

00:00:28.189 --> 00:00:31.687
in verjamem, spet,

00:00:31.687 --> 00:00:33.226
da mi bo uspelo

00:00:33.226 --> 00:00:36.010
čez vso to široko,

00:00:36.010 --> 00:00:39.380
nevarno divjino oceana.

00:00:39.380 --> 00:00:41.127
Ne samo, da sem štirikrat poskusila,

00:00:41.127 --> 00:00:42.595
ampak najboljši plavalci na svetu

00:00:42.595 --> 00:00:45.599
poskušajo že od leta 1950,

00:00:45.599 --> 00:00:49.249
pa še zmeraj ni bilo storjeno.

00:00:49.249 --> 00:00:53.130
Ekipa je ponosna na naše štiri poskuse.

00:00:53.130 --> 00:00:55.684
To je ekspedicija okrog 30 ljudi.

00:00:55.684 --> 00:01:00.284
Bonnie je moja 
najboljša prijateljica in vodja,

00:01:00.284 --> 00:01:02.948
ki nekako prikliče voljo,

00:01:02.948 --> 00:01:06.731
zadnje kaplje volje v meni,
ko mislim, da je več ni,

00:01:06.731 --> 00:01:10.245
po mnogih, mnogih urah in dneh tam zunaj.

00:01:10.245 --> 00:01:12.716
Strokovnjaki za morske pse
so najboljši na svetu -

00:01:12.716 --> 00:01:16.598
veliki plenilci tam spodaj.

00:01:16.598 --> 00:01:19.959
Morska osa, ki ima
najbolj smrtonosen strup

00:01:19.959 --> 00:01:22.927
v vsem oceanu, je v teh vodah

00:01:22.927 --> 00:01:25.462
in zaradi njih sem skoraj umrla

00:01:25.462 --> 00:01:27.920
pri prejšnjem poskusu.

00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:30.356
Pogoji sami,

00:01:30.356 --> 00:01:33.301
poleg razdalje več kot 160 km

00:01:33.301 --> 00:01:35.588
na odprtem morju--

00:01:35.588 --> 00:01:38.133
tokovi in vrtinci,

00:01:38.133 --> 00:01:41.464
in Zalivski tok, najbolj nepredvidljiv

00:01:41.464 --> 00:01:45.432
na vsem planetu.

00:01:45.432 --> 00:01:49.445
Mimogrede, zabava me, da

00:01:49.445 --> 00:01:52.230
me novinarji in ljudje pred temi poskusi

00:01:52.230 --> 00:01:54.289
pogosto vprašajo,

00:01:54.289 --> 00:01:56.106
"Boš šla s kakšnim čolnom

00:01:56.106 --> 00:01:59.204
ali ljudmi ali kako?"

00:01:59.204 --> 00:02:01.364
Mislim si, kaj pa si predstavljajo?

00:02:01.364 --> 00:02:05.539
Da se bom orientirala po zvezdah

00:02:05.539 --> 00:02:09.211
in med zobmi imela nož,

00:02:09.211 --> 00:02:12.630
lovila ribe in jih žive odrla in jedla

00:02:12.630 --> 00:02:15.542
in mogoče še vlekla
napravo za razsoljevanje

00:02:15.542 --> 00:02:17.401
za sabo za svežo vodo.

00:02:17.401 --> 00:02:22.131
(Smeh)

00:02:22.131 --> 00:02:25.852
Ja, ekipo imam. (Smeh)

00:02:25.852 --> 00:02:30.195
Ekipa je strokovna, ekipa je pogumna

00:02:30.195 --> 00:02:32.700
in kar kipi od inovacij

00:02:32.700 --> 00:02:34.683
in znanstvenih odkritij,

00:02:34.683 --> 00:02:39.923
kot je pri vsaki veliki odpravi na svetu.

00:02:39.923 --> 00:02:42.760
Na potovanju smo.

00:02:42.760 --> 00:02:45.003
Debata je,

00:02:45.003 --> 00:02:46.383
že od Grkov dalje,

00:02:46.383 --> 00:02:49.067
mar ni to smisel vsega?

00:02:49.067 --> 00:02:51.435
Ni smisel življenja v potovanju,

00:02:51.435 --> 00:02:54.215
ne pa v destinaciji?

00:02:54.215 --> 00:02:55.667
Smo na tem potovanju

00:02:55.667 --> 00:02:58.226
in po pravici povedano
je bilo razburljivo.

00:02:58.226 --> 00:02:59.997
Nismo dosegli druge obale,

00:02:59.997 --> 00:03:03.749
a še vedno je tu naš ponos in predanost,

00:03:03.749 --> 00:03:05.808
neomajna predanost.

00:03:05.808 --> 00:03:10.366
Ko sem dopolnila 60 let,
so bile sanje še žive,

00:03:10.366 --> 00:03:12.319
od poskušanja v svojih dvajsetih,

00:03:12.319 --> 00:03:15.977
od sanj in načrtov.

00:03:15.977 --> 00:03:18.746
Najbolj znano vodno telo

00:03:18.746 --> 00:03:22.703
na svetu danes, si mislim,
od Kube to Floride.

00:03:22.703 --> 00:03:26.783
Globoko je bilo. Globoko v moji duši.

00:03:26.783 --> 00:03:29.363
Ko sem dopolnila 60 let,

00:03:29.363 --> 00:03:31.862
ni šlo toliko za atletski dosežek,

00:03:31.862 --> 00:03:35.179
ni bil to ego "Hočem biti prva".

00:03:35.179 --> 00:03:37.997
Vedno je tu in ne morem ga zanikati.

00:03:37.997 --> 00:03:41.755
A bilo je globlje. 
Bilo je, koliko življenja je še ostalo?

00:03:41.755 --> 00:03:44.940
Sprijaznimo se, vsi smo
na enosmerni cesti, kajne,

00:03:44.940 --> 00:03:46.586
in kaj bomo storili?

00:03:46.586 --> 00:03:48.727
Kaj bomo storili, ko gremo naprej,

00:03:48.727 --> 00:03:51.994
da bomo pri pogledu nazaj brez obžalovanj?

00:03:51.994 --> 00:03:54.656
In vsa pretekla leta treninga,

00:03:54.656 --> 00:03:57.367
sem imela citat Teddyja Roosevelta

00:03:57.367 --> 00:03:59.580
za parafrazo, vrtel se mi je po možganih

00:03:59.580 --> 00:04:01.483
in pravi: "Naprej greš,

00:04:01.483 --> 00:04:04.603
naprej greš in sediš
v svojem udobnem stolu

00:04:04.603 --> 00:04:08.584
in bodi kritik, bodi opazovalec,

00:04:08.584 --> 00:04:12.743
medtem ko gre tisti pogumni
v ring in se vplete

00:04:12.743 --> 00:04:15.388
in krvavi in se umaže in mu spodleti

00:04:15.388 --> 00:04:17.224
spet in spet in spet,

00:04:17.224 --> 00:04:19.660
a vseeno ga ni strah in ni plašen

00:04:19.660 --> 00:04:22.744
in živi življenje na drzen način."

00:04:22.744 --> 00:04:25.392
Seveda sem si želela priti čez.

00:04:25.392 --> 00:04:29.128
To je cilj in lahko sem
tako plehka, da rečem,

00:04:29.128 --> 00:04:32.594
da je bila letos destinacija še slajša

00:04:32.594 --> 00:04:34.101
od potovanja.

00:04:34.101 --> 00:04:39.357
(Smeh) (Aplavz)

00:04:39.357 --> 00:04:42.639
A vredno je bilo iti na to potovanje.

00:04:42.639 --> 00:04:45.206
Na tej točki, to poletje,

00:04:45.206 --> 00:04:48.671
vsi - znanstveniki, znanstveniki športa,

00:04:48.671 --> 00:04:53.230
strokovnjaki za vztrajnost, nevrologi,

00:04:53.230 --> 00:04:57.555
moja ekipa, Bonnie -

00:04:57.555 --> 00:04:59.453
so rekli, da je nemogoče.

00:04:59.453 --> 00:05:01.925
Enostavno je nemogoče
in Bonnie mi je rekla:

00:05:01.925 --> 00:05:03.964
"Ampak če boš šla na to potovanje,

00:05:03.964 --> 00:05:05.824
te bom pospremila do konca,

00:05:05.824 --> 00:05:07.299
tam bom."

00:05:07.299 --> 00:05:12.018
In zdaj smo tam.

00:05:12.018 --> 00:05:14.646
Ko gledamo ven, 
nekakšen surrealen trenutek,

00:05:14.646 --> 00:05:16.157
pred prvim zamahom,

00:05:16.157 --> 00:05:18.683
stojim na skalah Marine Hemingway,

00:05:18.683 --> 00:05:21.376
nad nami plapola zastava Kube,

00:05:21.376 --> 00:05:23.968
vsa moja ekipa v svojih čolnih,

00:05:23.968 --> 00:05:30.650
z rokami v zraku:
"Tu smo zate, tu smo zate,"

00:05:30.650 --> 00:05:32.655
Bonnie in jaz se spogledava in rečeva,

00:05:32.655 --> 00:05:34.610
letošnja mantra je -

00:05:34.610 --> 00:05:37.016
in uporabljali smo jo pri treningu -

00:05:37.016 --> 00:05:39.064
najdi pot.

00:05:39.064 --> 00:05:41.671
Imaš sanje

00:05:41.671 --> 00:05:44.686
in imaš ovire pred seboj, tako kot vsi.

00:05:44.686 --> 00:05:48.114
Nihče od nas ne gre skozi življenje

00:05:48.114 --> 00:05:51.759
brez srčnih bolečin,

00:05:51.759 --> 00:05:54.039
brez nemira,

00:05:54.039 --> 00:05:56.997
in če verjameš in imaš vero

00:05:56.997 --> 00:05:59.393
in če padeš in se spet pobereš

00:05:59.393 --> 00:06:02.318
in verjameš, da je vztrajnost

00:06:02.318 --> 00:06:05.848
krasna človeška lastnost,

00:06:05.848 --> 00:06:08.714
najdeš pot in Bonnie
me je zagrabila za ramena

00:06:08.714 --> 00:06:13.254
in rekla: "Najdiva pot na Florido."

00:06:13.254 --> 00:06:15.681
Začeli smo in naslednjih 53 ur

00:06:15.681 --> 00:06:21.447
je predstavljalo intenzivno, 
nepozabno življenjsko izkušnjo.

00:06:21.447 --> 00:06:23.688
Bili smo vzhičeni,

00:06:23.688 --> 00:06:25.911
nisem verna, a povem vam,

00:06:25.911 --> 00:06:29.648
biti v azurni modrini Zalivskega toka,

00:06:29.648 --> 00:06:31.390
ko dihaš,

00:06:31.390 --> 00:06:36.133
gledaš dol kilometre
in kilometre in kilometre

00:06:36.133 --> 00:06:40.872
in čutiš mogočnost tega modrega planeta,
na katerem živimo,

00:06:40.872 --> 00:06:44.400
navdušuje te.

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:47.420
Imam seznam približno 85 pesmi

00:06:47.420 --> 00:06:48.999
in še posebej sredi noči

00:06:48.999 --> 00:06:51.054
in ponoči, ker ne uporabljamo luči -

00:06:51.054 --> 00:06:53.854
svetloba privlači meduze,
morske pse,

00:06:53.854 --> 00:06:56.239
privlači ribe,
ki privlačijo morske pse,

00:06:56.239 --> 00:06:58.740
in tako gremo v popolnoma črni noči.

00:06:58.740 --> 00:07:02.143
Nikoli še niste videli črne,
ki bi bila tako črna.

00:07:02.143 --> 00:07:04.228
Ne vidiš sprednjega dela roke

00:07:04.228 --> 00:07:05.375
in ljudje v čolnu,

00:07:05.375 --> 00:07:07.170
Bonnie in moja ekipa v čolnu,

00:07:07.170 --> 00:07:09.227
samo zamahe rok slišijo

00:07:09.227 --> 00:07:10.439
in vedo, kje sem,

00:07:10.439 --> 00:07:12.498
ker se nič ne vidi.

00:07:12.498 --> 00:07:14.737
In jaz sem tam, uživam v

00:07:14.737 --> 00:07:16.521
svojem malem seznamu pesmi.

00:07:16.521 --> 00:07:19.049
(Smeh)

00:07:19.049 --> 00:07:21.025
Imam tesno gumijasto kapo,

00:07:21.025 --> 00:07:22.117
zato nič ne slišim.

00:07:22.117 --> 00:07:25.258
Imam očala in obračam glavo
50-krat na minuto

00:07:25.258 --> 00:07:27.300
in pojem,

00:07:27.300 --> 00:07:31.241
♪ Imagine there's no heaven ♪

00:07:31.241 --> 00:07:33.112
♪ doo doo doo doo doo ♪

00:07:33.112 --> 00:07:36.084
♪ It's easy if you try ♪

00:07:36.084 --> 00:07:37.417
♪ doo doo doo doo doo ♪

00:07:37.417 --> 00:07:39.810
In to pesem lahko zapojem 
tisočkrat zapovrstjo.

00:07:39.810 --> 00:07:42.129
(Smeh)

00:07:42.129 --> 00:07:44.945
No, to je talent že sam po sebi.

00:07:44.945 --> 00:07:49.307
(Smeh) (Aplavz)

00:07:49.307 --> 00:07:51.785
In vsakič, ko končam z

00:07:51.785 --> 00:07:58.650
♪ Ooh, you may say I'm a dreamer
but I'm not the only one ♪

00:07:58.650 --> 00:08:01.370
222.

00:08:01.370 --> 00:08:05.936
♪ Imagine there's no heaven ♪

00:08:05.936 --> 00:08:08.000
In ko pridem do konca tisoče

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:09.555
John Lennonove "Imagine",

00:08:09.555 --> 00:08:12.583
sem plavala devet ur in 45 minut,

00:08:12.583 --> 00:08:16.362
točno.

00:08:16.362 --> 00:08:20.454
In tu so tudi krize. Seveda so.

00:08:20.454 --> 00:08:22.537
Začne se bruhanje,

00:08:22.537 --> 00:08:24.099
morska voda, slabo ti je,

00:08:24.099 --> 00:08:27.611
nosiš masko proti meduzam
za največjo zaščito.

00:08:27.611 --> 00:08:29.215
Težko se plava v njej.

00:08:29.215 --> 00:08:31.779
Povzroča odrgnine znotraj ust,

00:08:31.779 --> 00:08:34.412
a lovke ne morejo do tebe.

00:08:34.412 --> 00:08:37.092
Pojavi se podhladitev.

00:08:37.092 --> 00:08:40.501
Voda ima 29°C in vseeno izgubljaš težo

00:08:40.501 --> 00:08:43.084
in porabljaš kalorije in ko prideš

00:08:43.084 --> 00:08:45.052
proti strani čolna,
ne smeš se ga dotakniti,

00:08:45.052 --> 00:08:46.084
ne smeš ven,

00:08:46.084 --> 00:08:48.824
a Bonnie in njena ekipa mi podata hrano

00:08:48.824 --> 00:08:52.176
in me vprašata, kaj delam, kako sem,

00:08:52.176 --> 00:08:57.708
jaz pa vidim Tadž Mahal tam.

00:08:57.708 --> 00:09:02.796
Sem v zelo drugačnem stanju

00:09:02.796 --> 00:09:06.335
in si mislim, vau, nisem si mislila,

00:09:06.335 --> 00:09:09.150
da bom tu naletela na Tadž Mahal.

00:09:09.150 --> 00:09:11.248
Prekrasen je.

00:09:11.248 --> 00:09:13.899
Mislim, kako dolgo so ga gradili?

00:09:13.899 --> 00:09:20.170
Res je--tako da, uuuu. (Smeh)

00:09:22.081 --> 00:09:24.318
Nekako imamo glavno pravilo,

00:09:24.318 --> 00:09:26.519
da mi nikdar ne povedo, kako daleč je še,

00:09:26.519 --> 00:09:27.811
ker ne vemo, kako daleč je še.

00:09:27.811 --> 00:09:29.143
Kaj se ti bo zgodilo

00:09:29.143 --> 00:09:30.921
med to točko in drugo točko.

00:09:30.921 --> 00:09:32.433
Kaj bo z vremenom

00:09:32.433 --> 00:09:35.624
in tokovi, in, bog ne daj, da te piči,

00:09:35.624 --> 00:09:38.906
ko misliš, da te v tem oklepu
nič ne more pičiti,

00:09:38.906 --> 00:09:41.413
in Bonnie se je odločila

00:09:41.413 --> 00:09:44.572
na prehodu v tretje jutro,

00:09:44.572 --> 00:09:46.550
da trpim

00:09:46.550 --> 00:09:50.106
in da visim na nitki

00:09:50.106 --> 00:09:51.569
in mi je rekla, "Pridi sem,"

00:09:51.569 --> 00:09:52.901
prišla sem bližje, rekla je,

00:09:52.901 --> 00:09:54.536
"Poglej, poglej tja,"

00:09:54.536 --> 00:09:57.605
Videla sem svetlobo,
ker je dan lažji od noči,

00:09:57.605 --> 00:09:59.458
in mislila sem, da gremo v dan,

00:09:59.458 --> 00:10:02.102
in sem videla tok bele svetlobe

00:10:02.102 --> 00:10:03.481
ob obzorju,

00:10:03.481 --> 00:10:05.508
in rekla: "Kmalu bo jutro."

00:10:05.508 --> 00:10:11.450
In rekla je: "Ne, to so luči Key Westa."

00:10:11.450 --> 00:10:13.423
Še 15 ur,

00:10:13.423 --> 00:10:15.949
kar bi bilo za večino plavalcev
dolgo časa.

00:10:15.949 --> 00:10:22.040
(Smeh) (Aplavz)

00:10:22.040 --> 00:10:26.708
Pojma nimate,
koliko 15-urnih treningov je za mano.

00:10:26.708 --> 00:10:30.426
Tako sem, nekako, brez odločitve,

00:10:30.426 --> 00:10:32.785
nehala šteti zamahe

00:10:32.785 --> 00:10:36.536
in nisem pela
ali citirala Stephena Hawkinga

00:10:36.536 --> 00:10:39.134
in parametrov vesolja,

00:10:39.134 --> 00:10:41.795
samo zatopila sem se
v premišljevanje o teh sanjah

00:10:41.795 --> 00:10:44.755
in zakaj in kako.

00:10:44.755 --> 00:10:48.154
Kot sem rekla, ko sem jih dopolnila 60,

00:10:48.154 --> 00:10:52.503
ni šlo več za konkretno "Zmoreš?"

00:10:52.503 --> 00:10:55.142
To so vsakdanji mehanizmi.

00:10:55.142 --> 00:10:57.765
To je disciplina in to so priprave

00:10:57.765 --> 00:10:59.642
in v tem je ponos.

00:10:59.642 --> 00:11:04.517
A odločila sem se, da bom mislila,

00:11:04.517 --> 00:11:08.042
izraz je ponavadi segati po zvezdah,

00:11:08.042 --> 00:11:11.118
v mojem primeru pa segam po obzorju.

00:11:11.118 --> 00:11:13.133
In ko dosežeš obzorje,

00:11:13.133 --> 00:11:16.043
kot sem dokazala, morda ne prideš do tja,

00:11:16.043 --> 00:11:22.028
a kakšno neverjetno 
utrjevanje karakterja in duha

00:11:22.028 --> 00:11:24.209
se zgodi.

00:11:24.209 --> 00:11:26.652
Kakšno osnovo zgradiš v seganju

00:11:26.652 --> 00:11:29.689
za temi obzorji.

00:11:29.689 --> 00:11:32.232
Sedaj prihaja obala

00:11:32.232 --> 00:11:35.238
in majhen del mene je žalosten.

00:11:35.238 --> 00:11:37.621
Epskega potovanja bo konec.

00:11:37.621 --> 00:11:39.452
Toliko ljudi zdaj pride do mene in reče:

00:11:39.452 --> 00:11:44.645
"Kaj pa bo naslednje? 
Super se nam je zdelo!

00:11:44.645 --> 00:11:46.805
Tisti sledilnik na računalniku?

00:11:46.805 --> 00:11:49.889
Kam greš naslednjič? Komaj čakamo,
da sledimo naslednji stvari."

00:11:49.889 --> 00:11:52.642
No, oni so bili tam 53 ur,

00:11:52.642 --> 00:11:55.030
jaz pa leta.

00:11:55.030 --> 00:11:58.547
Tako da ne bo še enega
epskega potovanja po oceanu.

00:11:58.547 --> 00:12:02.145
Ampak smisel je in smisel je bil,

00:12:02.145 --> 00:12:07.217
da je vsak naš dan epski,

00:12:07.217 --> 00:12:09.602
in povem vam, ko sem stopila na to obalo,

00:12:09.602 --> 00:12:11.710
se opotekla na to obalo,

00:12:11.710 --> 00:12:14.329
in sem tolikokrat

00:12:14.329 --> 00:12:18.110
z napihnjenim egom

00:12:18.110 --> 00:12:22.577
vadila, kaj bom povedala na obali.

00:12:22.577 --> 00:12:24.191
Ko je Bonnie mislila, da

00:12:24.191 --> 00:12:26.199
mi zateka grlo,

00:12:26.199 --> 00:12:28.161
in je k našemu čolnu
pripeljala zdravstveno ekipo,

00:12:28.161 --> 00:12:31.204
da jim je povedala,

00:12:31.204 --> 00:12:32.621
da s težavo diham.

00:12:32.621 --> 00:12:35.715
Še 12, 24 ur v slani vodi,

00:12:35.715 --> 00:12:37.410
vsa ta stvar - in pomislila sem

00:12:37.425 --> 00:12:42.157
v trenutku halucinacije,
da sem slišala besedo traheotomija.

00:12:42.157 --> 00:12:43.669
(Smeh)

00:12:43.669 --> 00:12:45.988
Bonnie je rekla zdravniku:

00:12:45.988 --> 00:12:47.766
"Ne skrbi me za njeno dihanje.

00:12:47.766 --> 00:12:49.525
Če ne bo mogla govoriti,
ko pride na obalo,

00:12:49.525 --> 00:12:51.614
bo pobesnela."

00:12:51.614 --> 00:12:55.305
(Smeh)

00:12:57.056 --> 00:12:59.731
A v resnici, vsi tisti govori

00:12:59.731 --> 00:13:02.194
ki sem jih vadila, samo da sem prišla čez

00:13:02.194 --> 00:13:04.741
nekaj treningov za motivacijo,

00:13:04.741 --> 00:13:06.233
ni bilo tako.

00:13:06.233 --> 00:13:08.776
Bil je zelo resničen trenutek,

00:13:08.776 --> 00:13:11.168
s to množico, z mojo ekipo.

00:13:11.168 --> 00:13:13.788
Uspelo nam je. Ne meni. Nam je uspelo.

00:13:13.788 --> 00:13:17.029
Tega ne bomo nikoli pozabili.
Vedno bo del nas.

00:13:17.029 --> 00:13:19.899
Tri stvari, ki sem jih nekako bleknila,

00:13:19.899 --> 00:13:24.350
ko sem prišla tja, so bile, prvič: 
"Nikoli, nikoli se ne vdajte."

00:13:24.350 --> 00:13:29.634
To živim. Kakšna je
današnja Sokratova fraza?

00:13:29.634 --> 00:13:31.219
Biti pomeni delati.

00:13:31.219 --> 00:13:34.326
Zato ne vstanem in rečem,
nikoli se ne vdaj.

00:13:34.326 --> 00:13:38.092
Tam se nisem vdala,
za temi besedami so bila dejanja.

00:13:38.092 --> 00:13:41.153
Drugič: "Sanje lahko lovite

00:13:41.153 --> 00:13:43.110
kadarkoli; 
nikoli niste prestari."

00:13:43.110 --> 00:13:47.232
Pri 64, česar ni nihče
katerekoli starosti, spola,

00:13:47.232 --> 00:13:48.915
zmogel, sem to storila,

00:13:48.915 --> 00:13:50.679
in ni dvoma,

00:13:50.679 --> 00:13:53.648
da sem danes na vrhuncu življenja.

00:13:53.648 --> 00:13:56.476
(Aplavz)

00:13:56.476 --> 00:13:59.294
Ja.

00:14:02.058 --> 00:14:03.881
Hvala.

00:14:03.881 --> 00:14:06.035
In tretja stvar,
ki sem jo rekla na plaži:

00:14:06.035 --> 00:14:08.724
"Izgleda kot 
najbolj samoten trud na svetu

00:14:08.724 --> 00:14:10.716
in na mnoge načine seveda je

00:14:10.716 --> 00:14:14.593
in na druge, najbolj pomembne načine,

00:14:14.593 --> 00:14:17.187
je to ekipa, 
in če mislite, da sem jaz huda,

00:14:17.187 --> 00:14:18.651
boste hoteli spoznati Bonnie.

00:14:18.651 --> 00:14:20.026
(Smeh)

00:14:20.026 --> 00:14:22.541
Bonnie, kje si?

00:14:22.541 --> 00:14:25.164
Kje si?

00:14:25.164 --> 00:14:28.954
To je Bonnie Stoll. (Aplavz)

00:14:28.954 --> 00:14:31.276
Moja kolegica.

00:14:33.072 --> 00:14:35.541
Kot pravi citat Henry David Thoreauja,

00:14:35.541 --> 00:14:38.575
ko dosežeš svoje sanje,
ne gre toliko za to, kaj dobiš,

00:14:38.575 --> 00:14:41.501
kot za to, kdo s tem postaneš.

00:14:41.501 --> 00:14:43.639
In ja, sedaj stojim pred vami.

00:14:43.639 --> 00:14:45.496
V treh mesecih po koncu plavanja

00:14:45.496 --> 00:14:47.450
sem sedela z Oprah

00:14:47.450 --> 00:14:51.191
in bila v Ovalni pisarni
predsednika Obame.

00:14:51.191 --> 00:14:54.686
Povabili so me, da govorim
pred skupinami ljudi, kot ste vi.

00:14:54.686 --> 00:14:57.396
Podpisala sem pogodbo za knjigo.

00:14:57.396 --> 00:15:00.033
Vse to je super, tega ne podcenjujem.

00:15:00.033 --> 00:15:01.860
Ponosna sem na vse to, ampak resnica je,

00:15:01.860 --> 00:15:04.808
naokrog hodim z dvignjeno glavo,
ker sem tista drzna

00:15:04.808 --> 00:15:09.232
neustrašna oseba in to bom, vsak dan,

00:15:09.232 --> 00:15:13.468
dokler ne napoči konec teh dni.

00:15:13.468 --> 00:15:15.688
Najlepša hvala in uživajte v konferenci.

00:15:15.688 --> 00:15:20.257
Hvala. Hvala. Hvala. (Aplavz)

00:15:20.257 --> 00:15:23.108
Hvala. Hvala. Hvala. Hvala.

00:15:23.108 --> 00:15:25.476
Hvala.

00:15:26.995 --> 00:15:30.697
Najdite pot! (Aplavz)

